Integration tests using integration test package.(WidgetTest)
=============================================================

Automated run:
in the admin directory, Moqui in:  growerpMoqui
flutter pub run utils:runIntegration.dart

On mobile.
----------

single test:
flutter drive  \
    --driver=test_driver/integration_test.dart \
    --target=integration_test/newCompany_test.dart
    
to run all tests with screenshot on error:
flutter drive --screenshot=. \
  --driver=test_driver/integration_test.dart \
  --target=integration_test/main_tests.dart 


on chrome
---------

Download chromedriver and install in path:
https://flutter.dev/docs/cookbook/testing/integration/introduction#6b-web

start in a terminal: ./chromedriver --port=4444

Separate terminal:

flutter drive  -d web-server \
    --no-headless \
    --driver=test_driver/integration_test.dart \
    --target=integration_test/newCompany_test.dart


Chat test
---------

1. make sure the debug company of John doe exists
2. start the chat echo: flutter run integration_test/chatEcho_test.dart
    and login with default debud parameters.
3. run the chat test in a separate process: 
flutter drive  \
    --driver=test_driver/integration_test.dart \
    --target=integration_test/chat_test.dart
    